Q: 提供2024年每月各个国家的飞行量及其环比增长或下降百分比。
SQL:
WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                a.dep_country_name,
                count(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN avigo_nlp_dev.ai_target_jet b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
        WHERE
                a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
                AND a.dep_country_name IS NOT NULL
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month,
                a.dep_country_name
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( SELECT *, lag( num ) over ( PARTITION BY dep_country_name ORDER BY date_month ) AS last_num FROM biao_1 ) SELECT
        date_month,
        dep_country_name,
        num,
        last_num,
        concat( round(( num - last_num )/ last_num * 100, 2 ), '%' ) AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
WHERE
        last_num IS NOT NULL;
actual_SQL:
WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                a.dep_country_name,
                count(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN avigo_nlp_dev.ai_target_jet b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
        WHERE
                a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
                AND a.dep_country_name IS NOT NULL
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month,
                a.dep_country_name
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( 
            SELECT *, 
            lag(num) OVER (PARTITION BY dep_country_name ORDER BY date_month) AS last_num 
            FROM biao_1 
        ) 
SELECT
        date_month,
        dep_country_name,
        num,
        last_num,
        CONCAT(ROUND((num - last_num) / last_num * 100, 2), '%') AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
WHERE
        last_num IS NOT NULL;
